# MacCode Store

A premium e-commerce platform built with Django, featuring a sleek modern frontend and a customized, administrative dashboard.

[![Django Version](https://img.shields.com/badge/Django-5.0%2B-green.svg)](https://www.djangoproject.com/)
[![Payment Processor](https://img.shields.com/badge/Payment-Stripe-blue.svg)](https://stripe.com/)
[![Admin Theme](https://img.shields.com/badge/Admin%20Theme-Unfold-purple.svg)](https://github.com/unfoldadmin/django-unfold)

---

## 🚀 Overview

MacCode Store is a full-stack e-commerce application designed to provide a seamless, premium shopping experience. It features dynamic product listings, a real-time shopping cart, a secured checkout pipeline, and a highly customized internal administrative dashboard. The project prioritizes modern user experience (UX), robust backend validation, and operational efficiency.

## ✨ Key Features

### 🛒 Frontend (User Experience)
* **Modern UI/UX:** Responsive design built with Bootstrap 5 and custom CSS3 animations.
* **Dynamic Cart:** Asynchronous product updates (Add, Qty Update, Remove) powered by AJAX/jQuery.
* **Sealed Checkout:** Secure checkout pipeline available exclusively to registered users.
* **Interactive Header:** Dynamic navbar featuring real-time cart counts and customized user avatars (initials/images).
* **Stripe Integration:** Proactive backend validation ensures transactions meet Stripe’s minimum threshold (₹50), providing a crash-free payment flow.

### 🛡️ Backend & Administration
* **Secured Authentication:** Fully implemented user registration, login (with safe redirects), and password reset flows.
* **Unfold Admin Panel:** A highly customized internal dashboard featuring a dark navy/purple theme (Tailwind CSS), optimized layouts, and improved data visualization.
* **Data Integrity:** Robust DecimalField configurations and transaction checks to handle high-value products securely.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* **Backend:** Python 3.x, Django 5.x
* **Database:** PostgreSQL (or SQLite for development)
* **Payment:** Stripe API (via `stripe-python`)
* **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript/jQuery, AJAX, Bootstrap 5
* **Admin Framework:** Django Unfold (Tailwind CSS)

## 🔧 Installation & Setup

### Prerequisites
* Python 3.x
* Pip
* A Stripe Account (for API keys)

### Step 1: Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone [https://github.com/yourusername/maccode_store.git](https://github.com/yourusername/maccode_store.git)
cd maccode_store